word.source: Our mission is to delight clients with quality hair products and legendary customer support. luvmehair hair knows that our consumers want authentic long lasting gorgeous hair. This is why we have strict requirements when selecting bundles of hair for you. By painstakingly hand selecting each batch of virgin hair, we can ensure and stand behind the quality. Our virgin hair does not tangle, shed, or breakdown over time. Besides the best quality, we are the first and few to offer 30 day returns, price matching guarantee, in-house live chat customer service available almost 24 hours/day, and free shipping.
word.translation: Notre mission est de ravir les clients avec des produits capillaires de qualité et de soutien à la clientèle légendaire. cheveux luvmehair sait que nos consommateurs veulent authentiques longs cheveux magnifiques durable.
